 Sia sues to expose identity thief trying to access her unreleased music https://www.nme.com/news/music/sia-sues-to-expose-identity-thief-trying-to-access-her-unreleased-music-3520976?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=sia-sues-to-expose-identity-thief-trying-to-access-her-unreleased-musicLiberty Dunworth Wed, 25 Oct 2023 08:55:33 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3520976 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sia@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Sia performs on the runway during the Christian Siriano SS24 Runway Show at The Pierre Hotel on September 08, 2023 in New York City" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sia@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sia@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sia@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sia@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sia@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sia@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> It comes after somebody has been sending emails posed as her, demanding access to unreleased recordings</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sia-sues-to-expose-identity-thief-trying-to-access-her-unreleased-music-3520976">Sia sues to expose identity thief trying to access her unreleased music</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sia@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Sia performs on the runway during the Christian Siriano SS24 Runway Show at The Pierre Hotel on September 08, 2023 in New York City" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sia@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sia@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sia@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sia@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sia@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sia@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sia">Sia</a> has filed a lawsuit in the hopes of exposing an identity thief who has been trying to access her unreleased music.</p><ul><li> <strong>READ MORE: <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sia-music-songs-from-and-inspired-by-the-motion-picture-review-2882539">Sia – &#39;Music – Songs from and Inspired by the Motion Picture&#39; review: better than the movie</a></strong></li></ul><p> The lawsuit has been filed against an unidentified John/Jane Doe defendant, who has been posing as the singer online and sending emails to industry insiders demanding access to her unreleased recordings.</p><p> Although the exact identity of the person is not yet known, the culprit is thought to be living in California and has been illegally contacting people working in the music industry over the last few months pretending to be the musician.</p><p> Sia – whose real name is Sia Kate Isobelle Furler – has launched the lawsuit in the hopes of obtaining records from any email providers used by the alleged perpetrator to send the fraudulent messages, and to expose the person responsible.</p><p> According to a report by <a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/sia-sues-identity-thief-1234860914/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Rolling Stone</em></a> , the complaint states that the “defendant has emailed a number of persons in the music industry with whom plaintiff is acquainted, including California residents, identifying him or herself as plaintiff, using an email address containing plaintiff&#39;s name”. It also adds that, under the guise of Sia, the person has been “fraudulently asking the acquaintances to send the person recordings of plaintiff performing that are not publicly available.” </p><figure id="attachment_3520988" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3520988" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3520988" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sia-live@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Sia performs at the 2020 MTV Movie &amp; TV Awards: Greatest Of All Time" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sia-live@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sia-live@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sia-live@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sia-live@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sia-live@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sia-live@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3520988" class="wp-caption-text"> Sia performs at the 2020 MTV Movie &amp; TV Awards: Greatest Of All Time. CREDIT: Kevin Mazur/2020 MTV Movie &amp; TV Awards/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> The &#39;Chandelier&#39; singer is seeking real and punitive damages for the alleged email spoofing, identity theft and invasion of privacy, as well as attorney fees.</p><p> The case is ongoing and Sia&#39;s lawyer has not yet publicly commented on the lawsuit.</p><p> In other Sia news, last month the singer-songwriter <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sia-shares-gimme-love-and-announces-first-album-in-eight-years-reasonable-woman-3497558">shared a new single titled &#39;Gimme Love&#39;</a> , taken from her forthcoming album &#39;Reasonable Woman&#39;.</p><p> Set for release in spring 2024 via Atlantic Records, the LP will mark her first full-length project in eight years, and can be pre-ordered <a href="https://eurostore.warnermusic.com/gb/music-store/artists/sia/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a> .</p><p> Additionally, she has also been <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paris-hilton-to-release-new-album-executive-produced-by-sia-3517198">working with Paris Hilton as the executive producer for the latter&#39;s upcoming album</a> and first full LP since 2006.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sia-sues-to-expose-identity-thief-trying-to-access-her-unreleased-music-3520976">Sia sues to expose identity thief trying to access her unreleased music</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
